msgstr "API 密钥不能为空。"

msgid "API returned HTTP %1$d. %2$s"
msgstr "API 返回 HTTP %1$d。%2$s"

msgid "API returned HTTP %d."
msgstr "API 返回 HTTP %d。"

msgid "No model configured."
msgstr "未配置模型。"

msgid "API request failed. Please check your settings."
msgstr "API 请求失败，请检查设置。"

msgid "Empty response from API."
msgstr "API 返回了空响应。"

msgid "All models failed."
msgstr "所有模型均失败。"

msgid "Invalid category or topic."
msgstr "无效的分类或主题。"

msgid "Write a detailed, engaging section for the heading: \"%1$s\"\n\nFull outline context:\n%2$s\n\n%3$s\n\nWrite in a professional yet accessible tone. Use markdown formatting. The section should be 300-500 words."
msgstr "为标题 \"%1$s\" 撰写一个详细、引人入胜的章节。\n\n完整大纲上下文：\n%2$s\n\n%3$s\n\n请使用专业但易于理解的语调，使用 Markdown 格式。章节字数应在 300-500 字。"

msgid "Focus on these keywords: %s"
msgstr "关注以下关键词：%s"

msgid "Based on the following article, suggest 3 to 5 relevant tags as a JSON array of strings. Only return the JSON array, nothing else.\n\nArticle:\n%s"
msgstr "根据以下文章，建议 3 到 5 个相关标签，以 JSON 字符串数组格式返回。只返回 JSON 数组，不要返回其他内容。\n\n文章：\n%s"

msgid "Create a detailed article outline for the topic \"%1$s\" in the category \"%2$s\".%3$s%4$s\n\nReturn the outline in markdown format with H2 headings and brief bullet points under each. Include an introduction and conclusion section."
msgstr "为分类 \"%2$s\" 下的主题 \"%1$s\" 创建详细的文章大纲。%3$s%4$s\n\n以 Markdown 格式返回大纲，使用 H2 标题和简短的要点。包含引言和结论部分。"

msgid "Write a complete, well-structured article about \"%1$s\" in the category \"%2$s\".%3$s%4$s\n\nRequirements:\n- Use proper headings (H1 for title, H2 for sections)\n- Include an introduction and conclusion\n- Write in a professional yet engaging tone\n- Aim for 800-1500 words\n- Use markdown formatting"
msgstr "撰写一篇关于分类 \"%2$s\" 下主题 \"%1$s\" 的完整、结构清晰的文章。%3$s%4$s\n\n要求：\n- 使用适当的标题（H1 为文章标题，H2 为章节标题）\n- 包含引言和结论\n- 使用专业且引人入胜的语调\n- 目标 800-1500 字\n- 使用 Markdown 格式"

msgid "You are a professional content writer for a WordPress blog. Write clear, engaging, and SEO-friendly content. Always respond in the same language as the user's request."
msgstr "你是一位专业的 WordPress 博客内容撰稿人。请撰写清晰、引人入胜且 SEO 友好的内容。始终使用与用户请求相同的语言回复。"

